e-content \"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">What is it?</h4><p class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Traditional outdoor off-leash areas where dogs can run freely and socialize with other dogs.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Key Features</h4><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d features-chips\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Fenced enclosures</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Open grass areas</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Agility equipment</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Water stations</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Waste disposal</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Best For</h4><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-list\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">High-energy dogs</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">Social dogs</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">Owners looking for free exercise options</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">What to Bring</h4><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-list\"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Leash (for entering/exiting)</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Water bowl</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21f