and Boutique.  What makes this dog facility special is its knowledgeable, trustworthy, amazing. The staff's dedication to creating a positive experience for both dogs and their owners is evident in every visit. i can’t say enough amazing things about wag it better and their training program This facility specializes in Pet care and Professional services. For more information, call (615) 410-7393. Visit their website at http://www.wagitbetter.com/ to learn more about their services and pricing.\",\"slug\":\"wag-it-better-family-dog-training-and-boutique\",\"address\":\"215 Robert Rose Dr\",\"street\":\"215 Robert Rose Dr\",\"city\":\"Murfreesboro\",\"state\":\"TN\",\"zipCode\":\"37128\",\"full_address\":\"215 Robert Rose Dr, Murfreesboro, TN 37128, USA\",\"latitude\":35.850475,\"longitude\":-86.42287,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJQ_ZlMWEPZIgRpV8xG7UTMGQ\",\"phone\":\"(615) 410-7393\",\"website\":\"http://www.wagitbetter.com/\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.9,\"reviewCount\":79,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"10:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"10:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"10:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"10:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"10:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"10:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"Closed\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":true,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"}],\"cityName\":\"Murfreesboro\",\"insightCards\":\"$undefined\",\"topAmenities\":[{\"key\":\"Onsite services\",\"label\":\"Onsite services\",\"count\":39,\"share\":100},{\"key\":\"Indoor facilities\",\"label\":\"Indoor facilities\",\"count\":39,\"share\":100},{\"key\":\"Professional staff\",\"label\":\"Profe