th: 768px) 100vw, 540px\",\"unoptimized\":true}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-image-gradient\"}]]}]}]\n14:[\"$\",\"$L27\",null,{\"city\":\"Murfreesboro\",\"state\":\"TN\"}]\n15:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"city-insights\",\"className\":\"city-insights-section\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-shell\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L28\",null,{\"parks\":[{\"id\":\"ChIJ_Rg38GMHZIgRZsblS-9m8VU\",\"name\":\"Affordable Dog Grooming\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"Affordable Dog Grooming has become a favorite among the area residents.  What makes this dog facility special is its great. ammo loves audra and she does a great job This facility specializes in Pet care and Professional services. For more information, call (615) 692-8490. Visit their website at https://www.affordabledoggroomingboro.com/ to learn more about their services and pricing.\",\"slug\":\"affordable-dog-grooming\",\"address\":\"2311 Hillmont Dr\",\"street\":\"2311 Hillmont Dr\",\"city\":\"Murfreesboro\",\"state\":\"TN\",\"zipCode\":\"37129\",\"full_address\":\"2311 Hillmont Dr, Murfreesboro, TN 37129, USA\",\"latitude\":35.87917960000001,\"longitude\":-86.4051526,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJ_Rg38GMHZIgRZsblS-9m8VU\",\"phone\":\"(615) 692-8490\",\"website\":\"https://www.affordabledoggroomingboro.com/\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.8,\"reviewCount\":6,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"7:00 AM – 1:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"7:00 AM – 1:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"7:00 AM – 1:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"7:00 AM – 1:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"Closed\",\"Saturday\":\"Closed\",\"Sunday\":\"Closed\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":false,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJwVbwNhreBWIRj4kw6r3IIIU\",\"name\":\"Always Training K9s\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in the area rave about Always Training K9s.  What makes this dog facility special is its amazing, great, knowledgeable. The staff's dedication to creating a positive experience for both dogs and their owners is evident in every visit. nikki has been amazing for our new puppy billie This facility specializes in Pet care and Professional services. For more information, call (615) 648-7590. Visit their website at https://www.alwaystrainingk9s.com/ to learn more about their services and pricing.\",\"slug\":\"always-training-k9s\",\"address\":\"114 Leland Ct E\",\"street\":\"114 Leland Ct E\",\"city\":\"Murfreesboro\",\"state\":\"TN\",\"zipCode\":\"37128\",\"full_address\":\"114 Leland Ct E, Murfreesboro, TN 37128, USA\",\"latitude\":35.77108919999999,\"longitude\":-86.4551863,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJwVbwNhreBWIRj4kw6r3IIIU\",\"phone\":\"(615) 648-7590\",\"website\":\"https://www.alwaystrainingk9s.com/\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":5,\"reviewCount\":41,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"8:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"8:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"8:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"8:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"8:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"8:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"Closed\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":false,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJ-QMtBf32Y4gRschuqSKSEbg\",\"name\":\"Animal Care Veterinary Hospital\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in the area rave about Animal Care Veterinary Hospital.  What makes this veterinary care special is its clean, excellent, amazing. The staff's dedication to creating a positive experience for both dogs and their owners is evident in every visit. my pup is always so soft and clean and smells amazing for days Located in a safe area, This facility specializes in Pet care and Professional services. For more information, call (615) 896-3434. Visit their website at https://animalcarevet.net/?utm_source=gmb&utm_medium=organic to learn more about their services and pricing.\",\"slug\":\"animal-care-veterinary-hospital\",\"address\":\"2750 New Salem Hwy\",\"street\":\"2750 New Salem Hwy\",\"city\":\"Murfreesboro\",\"state\":\"TN\",\"zipCode\":\"37128\",\"full_address\":\"2750 New Salem Hwy, Murfreesboro, TN 37128, USA\",\"latitude\":35.81085239999999,\"longitude\":-86.4613168,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJ-QMtBf32Y4gRschuqSKSEbg\",\"phone\":\"(615) 896-3434\",\"website\":\"https://animalcarevet.net/?utm_source=gmb&utm_medium=organic\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.8,\"reviewCount\":837,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"7:00 AM – 5:30 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"7:00 AM – 5:30 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"7:00 AM – 5:30 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"7:00 AM – 5:30 PM\",\"Friday\":\"7:00 AM – 5:30 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"7:00 AM – 12:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"Closed\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":true,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJ6frwyPH5Y4gRIqgS8qZhlk4\",\"name\":\"BB Dog Farm Pickup Location\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"Pet parents in the area rave about BB Dog Farm Pickup Location.  What mak